{"tid":154022,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"點解逢親有衝突實有人走出黎話兩邊都有錯","createTime":"2017-03-13T04:03:00.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-14T09:19:45.000Z","uid":65328,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8b1c5be284e76a16634f7b055d3370e215f8beb9","tid":154022,"uid":65328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T04:03:01.000Z","msg":"點解逢親有衝突實有人走出黎話兩邊都有錯？<br />\n結婚化妝師單野， 就有好多人走出黎話<br />\n&quot;新娘仆街， 但化妝師實有唔著&quot;類似既說話。<br />\n<br />\n其實衣班人係咪弱智定無點讀過書，<br />\n係咪無聽過&quot;恩將仇報&quot;,  &quot;忘恩負義&quot;,  &quot;人性本惡&quot; 等字？<br />\n<br />\n仆街就係仆街， 仆街做仆街野係天性， 你點做佢都會繼續做仆街。<br />\n<br />\n好似有d港女咁， 佢唔鐘意你，你做幾多野佢都唔鐘意你， 相反佢鐘意你， 你點仆街趕佢， 佢都係咁愛你。<br />\n<br />\n所以我真係好憎衣班<br />\n&quot;偽中立理性左膠大愛撚&quot;"},{"pid":"31fb9c65e45fae94bad2d61acd58e843863c7a19","tid":154022,"uid":83496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T04:04:41.000Z","msg":"信就信 唔信就唔信<br />\n乜撚野係微信<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9bcb59b8e1b6ed6c373b3f90ddf1c889a7ca14c2","tid":154022,"uid":35370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T04:04:44.000Z","msg":"佢哋知道企邊邊都會比人屌<br />\n所以想揀中立等兩邊都唔屌佢<br />\n結果係兩面不是人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1dd8a0570123defeaf0f020c8fb4bfff19962072","tid":154022,"uid":78785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T04:05:45.000Z","msg":"咁....兩邊都有錯唔代表佢就係中立架喎。<br />\n<br />\n支持一邊都可以指出佢既錯既....<br />\n<br />\n唔是咁非黑即白既"},{"pid":"f93e26baccb6b9f6a9be9e5440b17494df8a1b09","tid":154022,"uid":61106,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T04:07:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>信就信 唔信就唔信<br />\n乜撚野係微信<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5602cbae3f3ac51bd83ec5ff962aec9711f1cdf4","tid":154022,"uid":70538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-1